name: Chapter 1: The Maze
description:
“You wake up and don't remember anything. Your body hurts and your head is exploding...

Who are you? Where are you? These walls look old, very old..

You can't see an exit and a shiver runs down your spine when you hear a gruesome sound behind you.

You have to move on... You have to find a way out..“


----------------------------------------------

I hope you enjoy this interactive NFT. It was made for PC/Mac Browsers, however it also works on mobile devices with some constraints on the interaction.

Don’t miss this first chapter and the next ones :)

Have fun!!
